-)System Setting
Settings that apply to the entire Liferay installation, no matter how many instances exist.
They affect all instance, all sites, and all users.

Example Use Cases:
1)Configure email engine (SMTP settings for all instances)
2)Eable/disable CAPTCHA globally
3)Configure Elasticsearch or database connection
4)Global logging and scheduler settings
5)Global workflow engine


-)Instance Setting 
Settings that apply to a single Liferay instance (one tenant/domain).
Each instance has its own configuration, independent of others.
